Text: RE Energy Finance Conference participation Feb you We look forward to having you here Sincerely Angela Angela Dorsey Assistant Director Center for Energy Finance Education Research The University of Texas at Austin Department of Finance CBA Austin TX Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday January PM To Angela Dorsey Cc Subject Re Energy Finance Conference participation Feb Angela Thanks for your message I shall be glad to attend the conference both days I shall call Dr Ronn to discuss my participation Vince Kaminski Angela Dorsey on PM To Vincent Kaminski Email cc Subject Energy Finance Conference participation Feb Vince Further to Dr Ronns email dated please confirm your participation in the UT Energy Finance Conference to be held on the University of Texas campus Feb rd Sincerely Angela Angela Dorsey Assistant Director Center for Energy Finance Education Research The University of Texas at Austin Department of Finance CBA Austin TX

Energy Finance Conference presentations availableYou can now retrieve most all the speaker presentations of the Energy Finance Conference Feb from our website at with the exception of presentations made by John McCormack Peter Nance Sailesh Ramamurtie and Ehud Ronn Anoop Kapoor which I hope to still receive Sincerely Angela Angela Dorsey Assistant Director Center for Energy Finance Education Research The University of Texas at Austin Department of Finance CBA Austin TX
